---
// Hero section for Планометрика landing
// Dark gradient background with white text
---

<section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0A4C76] via-[#1A7BB3] to-[#0A4C76]">
  <!-- Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='0.4'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;); background-size: 60px 60px;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 py-20 text-center">
    <!-- Headline -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
      AI-платформа проектирования
      <span class="block mt-2">индивидуальных домов</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Для тех, кто строит свой дом. Для архитекторов, которые проектируют для клиентов.
      <span class="block mt-1">Для компаний, которые встраивают проектирование в свои продукты.</span>
    </p>

    <!-- CTA Buttons -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center mb-16">
      <!-- Primary CTA: Accent Green -->
      <a
        href="https://studio.planometrica.ru"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-[#0A4C76] bg-[#92CF93] rounded-xl hover:bg-[#7ec07f] transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      >
        Создать свой дом
        <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
        </svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Secondary CTA: Glass outline -->
      <a
        href="/planocad"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white/30 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-200"
      >
        Для профессионалов
      </a>

      <!-- Ghost CTA -->
      <a
        href="/partners"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-4 text-lg text-white/70 hover:text-white underline-offset-4 hover:underline transition-all duration-200"
      >
        Стать партнёром
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-8 border-t border-white/20">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1">10 стилей</div>
        <div class="text-white/70 text-sm">Архитектурных стилей</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1">25 сек</div>
        <div class="text-white/70 text-sm">AI-генерация планировки</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1">18 000+</div>
        <div class="text-white/70 text-sm">Нормативных документов</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1">от 490 ₽</div>
        <div class="text-white/70 text-sm">СПОЗУ готов за 1 день</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white/60" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
